Root cause: Server Components cannot pass functions as props to Client Components because functions are not serializable across the server/client boundary.

Fix: Convert the function call into a Server Action and pass the action reference:

```tsx
// app/page.tsx (Server Component)
import ClientComponent from './ClientComponent'
import { saveData } from './actions'

export default async function Page() {
  const data = await fetchData()
  return <ClientComponent saveAction={saveData} data={data} />
}

